high_descs: Turn around, move to the counter on the right, left of the sink.
Pick up the potato on the counter, left of the sink.
Turn around, bring the potato to the microwave on the right.
Heat the potato in the microwave.
Pick up the heated potato from the microwave, turn right, bring the heated potato to the coffee machine, turn left to face the shelf.
Put the heated potato on the shelf, left of of the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated potato on the shelf.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the sink on your right.
Pick up the potato from the sink.
Turn left and walk to the microwave above the dishwasher.
Microwave the potato and then pick up the potato from the microwave and close the microwave.
Turn right and walk to the lettuce on the shelf above the coffee machine.
Place the potato to the left of the lettuce on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved potato to the left of the lettuce on the shelf.

high_descs: Turn around, walk across the kitchen, turn right to face the sink.
Pick up the potato next to the spoon.
Turn around, walk towards the microwave on the right, face the microwave.
Place the potato to the left of the egg on the plate in the microwave, heat the microwave
Take out the potato from the microwave, turn right towards the sink, turn left to face the lettuce on the counter.
Place the potato next to the lettuce on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place the cooked potato next to the lettuce on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the sink on the right.
Pick up the potato.
Turn left and walk to the microwave.
Place the potato on the plate in the microwave that also has an egg on it. Heat them up.
Pick up the potato out of the microwave.
Take a step right and put the potato to the left of the lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated potato on a counter.

high_descs: Turn around, move across the room.  Turn to the right and face the counter by the sink.
Pick up the potato by the sink.
Do an about face, move forward until you reach the dishwasher on your right.  Turn to the counter above the dishwasher where there is a microwave.
Open the microwave and place the potato inside. Cook the potato and take it out of the microwave.
Turn around back toward the counter and the sink.  On the left there is a shelf above the counter.
Place the potato on the shelf by the lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Cook a potato.  Place it on the shelf by the lettuce.
